<p>Go to <strong>Setup » Orders » Order types » Subscription</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings. Take into account the explanations given in <a href="#table-subscription-default-settings">Table 1</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> (<span class="icon "><i class="fa fa-save  "></i></span>) the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
