<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="400">2.2. Creating order items</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>To complete the creation of the subscription, items have to be added. Only then will the subscription be saved and created. To do so, proceed as follows.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Adding items:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Add</strong> (<span class="icon "><i class="fa fa-plus-square  "></i></span>) in the section <strong>Order items</strong>.<br>
→ You are redirected to the <strong>items</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Set the filters for the search and also take the explanations given in <a href="#table-filters-item-search-redistribution">[table-filters-item-search-redistribution]</a> into account.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Execute the search by clicking on <strong>Search</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>If you want to delete the selected filters, click on <strong>Reset</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
